channel.title: "How do I...?" Quiz
channel.description:
1. How do I [b]add[/b] and [b]delete[/b] global objects? Global objects are visible things around Runescape e.g. Tree, gate.
2. How do I put together the dwarf cannon?
3. How do I make different spots PK-Able and Non PK-Able? e.g. Varrock banks PK-able, and Varrock Square non PK-able.
4. How do I find out the GFX IDs? (stillgfx(369) is the Ice Berage GFX. What tells us that?)
5. How do I make a full working Castle Wars arena? (Please post a link to the tutorial. I've tried looking but I haven't found one yet.)
6. How do I make the max stat [b]99[/b]? (Please post a link to the tutorial. I've tried looking but I haven't found one yet.)[br][size=1]Posted on: May 01, 2007, 12:38:42 AM[/size][hr]Sorry, you [b]don't[/b] have to answer all. Just one will be sweet. Thanks.[br][size=1]Posted on: May 01, 2007, 01:53:03 AM[/size][hr]Guys?
